{"type": "article", "id": 25494, "title": "无指针时钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-15T07:10:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153205yn7U4IkBNqurdcXV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这面钟已经完全取消了指针变成一个空心的圆环，它是用 ABS 塑料制作的。指示时间是采用亮灯的形式，亮数字灯表示小时，外圈的小格子则表示分钟，很简单。但显然它指示的是一个大概的时间，而这种较为模糊的方式也许不会让你感到时间的压力。可以通过按钮设定闹钟。钟直径有 30 厘米，有黑白两色可选，<a href=\"http://www.kibardindesign.com/e-shop/only-clock-original-kibardin/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021532013Mz0YigsPRZDu4KO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.35333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021532014NcmlDiIXGef0swQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.29714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153202UeMVNGBSjAwf9p26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153203zwv6sELgnRcOrkyb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153204YZzfUk3pOC627iG8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153204mChqnDXjKAvodWu7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153205CH1X85viqP6yMKmu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}